{
  "video_id": "o_U-_akINwQ",
  "title": "What should electric cars sound like? | Renzo Vitale",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13289.0,
      "end_time": 15373.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s start with silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 23280.0,
      "end_time": 27512.0,
      "text": "Silence is one of the most precious conditions for humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 27537.0,
      "end_time": 30901.0,
      "text": "because it allows us to feel the depth of our presence."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 32720.0,
      "end_time": 35310.0,
      "text": "This is one of the reasons why the advent of electric cars"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 35334.0,
      "end_time": 38207.0,
      "text": "has generated lots of enthusiasm among people."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 38679.0,
      "end_time": 43560.0,
      "text": "For the first time, we could associate the concept of cars"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 43800.0,
      "end_time": 44841.0,
      "text": "with the experience of silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 45824.0,
      "end_time": 47849.0,
      "text": "Cars can finally be quiet:"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 48770.0,
      "end_time": 50223.0,
      "text": "peace in the streets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 50247.0,
      "end_time": 52659.0,
      "text": "a silent revolution in the cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 56762.0,
      "end_time": 63143.0,
      "text": "(Hum)"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 65659.0,
      "end_time": 67826.0,
      "text": "But silence can also be a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 68801.0,
      "end_time": 72779.0,
      "text": "The absence of sound, in fact, when it comes to cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 72803.0,
      "end_time": 74880.0,
      "text": "it can be quite dangerous."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 74907.0,
      "end_time": 76946.0,
      "text": "Think of blind people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 76970.0,
      "end_time": 79152.0,
      "text": "who can&#39;t see a car which is approaching."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 80666.0,
      "end_time": 83295.0,
      "text": "And now, if it&#39;s electric, they can&#39;t even hear it."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 84380.0,
      "end_time": 87398.0,
      "text": "Or think of every one of us as we are walking around the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 87422.0,
      "end_time": 91323.0,
      "text": "we are absorbed in our thoughts, and we detach from the surroundings."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 92630.0,
      "end_time": 97270.0,
      "text": "In these situations, sound can become our precious companion."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 98552.0,
      "end_time": 103840.0,
      "text": "Sound is one of the most wonderful gifts of our universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 103108.0,
      "end_time": 104306.0,
      "text": "Sound is emotion"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 105259.0,
      "end_time": 106822.0,
      "text": "and sound is sublime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 108329.0,
      "end_time": 111648.0,
      "text": "and when it comes to cars, sound is also information."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 113606.0,
      "end_time": 115536.0,
      "text": "In order to protect pedestrians"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 115560.0,
      "end_time": 118535.0,
      "text": "and to give acoustic feedback to the drivers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 118559.0,
      "end_time": 122771.0,
      "text": "governments around the world have introduced several regulations"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 122795.0,
      "end_time": 126604.0,
      "text": "which prescribe the presence of a sound for electric vehicles."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 127454.0,
      "end_time": 131248.0,
      "text": "In particular, they require minimum sound levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 131272.0,
      "end_time": 133441.0,
      "text": "at specific frequency bands"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 133465.0,
      "end_time": 136400.0,
      "text": "up to the speed of 30 kilometers per hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 137798.0,
      "end_time": 139290.0,
      "text": "Besides this speed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 139530.0,
      "end_time": 142710.0,
      "text": "the natural noise of the car is considered as sufficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 144999.0,
      "end_time": 148585.0,
      "text": "These regulations have generated different reactions"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 148610.0,
      "end_time": 152587.0,
      "text": "among those who favor sounds and those who fear the presence"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 152611.0,
      "end_time": 154284.0,
      "text": "of too much noise in the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 155739.0,
      "end_time": 160429.0,
      "text": "However, I don&#39;t see it as the noise of the car."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 161792.0,
      "end_time": 165400.0,
      "text": "I rather see it as the voice of the car."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 166422.0,
      "end_time": 170900.0,
      "text": "And this is one of my biggest challenges, and privileges, at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 170954.0,
      "end_time": 173350.0,
      "text": "I design the voice of electric cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 175800.0,
      "end_time": 179279.0,
      "text": "We all know how a combustion engine sounds like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 179303.0,
      "end_time": 182625.0,
      "text": "and we do actually also know how an electric engine sounds like."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 183276.0,
      "end_time": 185435.0,
      "text": "Think of the electric tramway."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 185459.0,
      "end_time": 186673.0,
      "text": "As soon as it moves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 186697.0,
      "end_time": 190496.0,
      "text": "it creates this ascending high-frequency pitch sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 190520.0,
      "end_time": 192387.0,
      "text": "which we called \"whistling\" sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 193907.0,
      "end_time": 197249.0,
      "text": "However, if we would just amplify this sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 197273.0,
      "end_time": 201590.0,
      "text": "we would still not be able to fulfill the legal requirements."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 201830.0,
      "end_time": 204448.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s also why we need to compose new sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 205481.0,
      "end_time": 207551.0,
      "text": "So how do we go after it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 209178.0,
      "end_time": 212716.0,
      "text": "In many cities, the traffic is already very chaotic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 212740.0,
      "end_time": 214352.0,
      "text": "and we don&#39;t need more chaos."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 215221.0,
      "end_time": 220298.0,
      "text": "But the streets of the 21st century are a great case study"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 220322.0,
      "end_time": 224520.0,
      "text": "teeming with transience, cross purposes and disarray."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 225337.0,
      "end_time": 228591.0,
      "text": "And this landscape offers a great opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 228616.0,
      "end_time": 232806.0,
      "text": "for developing new solutions on how to reduce this chaos."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 234663.0,
      "end_time": 239133.0,
      "text": "I have conceived a new approach that tries to reduce the chaos"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 239157.0,
      "end_time": 240924.0,
      "text": "by introducing harmony."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 242898.0,
      "end_time": 247410.0,
      "text": "Since many people don&#39;t know how an electric car could sound like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 247650.0,
      "end_time": 251353.0,
      "text": "I have to define, first of all, a new sound world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 251378.0,
      "end_time": 255300.0,
      "text": "something that doesn&#39;t belong to our previous experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 255550.0,
      "end_time": 257521.0,
      "text": "but creates a reference for the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 259720.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263397.0,
      "text": "Together with a small team, we create lots of sonic textures"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 263421.0,
      "end_time": 267159.0,
      "text": "that are able to transmit emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 268640.0,
      "end_time": 270237.0,
      "text": "Just like a painter with colors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 270261.0,
      "end_time": 274734.0,
      "text": "we are able to connect feelings and frequencies"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 274758.0,
      "end_time": 277238.0,
      "text": "so that whenever one is approaching a car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 277262.0,
      "end_time": 279770.0,
      "text": "we can feel an emotion"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 279101.0,
      "end_time": 283700.0,
      "text": "which, besides fulfilling the legal requirements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 283310.0,
      "end_time": 286982.0,
      "text": "speaks also about the character and the identity of the car."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 289837.0,
      "end_time": 292941.0,
      "text": "I call this paradigm \"sound genetics.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 294433.0,
      "end_time": 300770.0,
      "text": "With sound genetics, I define, first of all, an aesthetic space of sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 300101.0,
      "end_time": 304303.0,
      "text": "and at the same time, I search for new, innovative methods"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 304327.0,
      "end_time": 307140.0,
      "text": "for generating soundscapes that we don&#39;t know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 308533.0,
      "end_time": 313191.0,
      "text": "soundscapes that allow us to envision abstract worlds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 314830.0,
      "end_time": 316128.0,
      "text": "to make them tangible and audible."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 318420.0,
      "end_time": 321427.0,
      "text": "Sound genetics is based on three steps."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 322266.0,
      "end_time": 325959.0,
      "text": "The first one is the definition of a sonic organism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 327313.0,
      "end_time": 330892.0,
      "text": "the second one is a description of sonic variations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 331884.0,
      "end_time": 336130.0,
      "text": "and the third one is the composition of sound genes."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 338732.0,
      "end_time": 344427.0,
      "text": "The description of a sonic organism is based on a cluster of properties"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 344451.0,
      "end_time": 347828.0,
      "text": "that every sound that I compose should have."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 350804.0,
      "end_time": 352316.0,
      "text": "[Sound is moving.]"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 352341.0,
      "end_time": 357601.0,
      "text": "I transfer to a small sound entity, such as the sound of a car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 358410.0,
      "end_time": 361339.0,
      "text": "the power of the motion of music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 361363.0,
      "end_time": 362957.0,
      "text": "so that sound can move so."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 364313.0,
      "end_time": 365698.0,
      "text": "[Sound is acting.]"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 365722.0,
      "end_time": 367640.0,
      "text": "And just like a dancer on a stage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 367665.0,
      "end_time": 371895.0,
      "text": "sound will project trajectories of sound in the air."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 374287.0,
      "end_time": 375438.0,
      "text": "[Sound is memory.]"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 375462.0,
      "end_time": 377625.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just about the sound of a car."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 378448.0,
      "end_time": 381423.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the memory of my father coming back home."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 383737.0,
      "end_time": 385274.0,
      "text": "[Sound is hypnotizing.]"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 385298.0,
      "end_time": 390949.0,
      "text": "And sound has the power to create an unexpected sense of wonder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 390973.0,
      "end_time": 392400.0,
      "text": "which hypnotizes."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 394400.0,
      "end_time": 395171.0,
      "text": "And ultimately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 395195.0,
      "end_time": 396670.0,
      "text": "[Sound is superhuman.]"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 396694.0,
      "end_time": 398694.0,
      "text": "sound goes beyond the human condition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 398718.0,
      "end_time": 401361.0,
      "text": "because it allows us to transcend."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 404544.0,
      "end_time": 408844.0,
      "text": "As a second step, we define the sonic variations."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 409297.0,
      "end_time": 410471.0,
      "text": "[Identity prism]"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 410495.0,
      "end_time": 414594.0,
      "text": "Just like humans, where different bodies generate different voices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 414618.0,
      "end_time": 419872.0,
      "text": "also different car shapes have a different acoustic behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 419896.0,
      "end_time": 422665.0,
      "text": "which depends on the geometry and the materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 423849.0,
      "end_time": 430630.0,
      "text": "So we have to know, first of all, how this car propagates the sound outside"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 430870.0,
      "end_time": 431998.0,
      "text": "by means of acoustic measurements."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 433650.0,
      "end_time": 439443.0,
      "text": "And just like a single voice is able to produce different tones and timbres,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 439467.0,
      "end_time": 442912.0,
      "text": "at the same time, we produce different sonic variations"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 442936.0,
      "end_time": 447229.0,
      "text": "within a space of eight words that I defined."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 448740.0,
      "end_time": 450921.0,
      "text": "And some of them are, to me, really important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 450945.0,
      "end_time": 453209.0,
      "text": "such as the concept of \"visionary,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 453233.0,
      "end_time": 456649.0,
      "text": "of \"elegance,\" of \"dynamic,\" of \"embracing.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 459757.0,
      "end_time": 462931.0,
      "text": "And once we have defined these two aspects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 462955.0,
      "end_time": 466100.0,
      "text": "we have what I call the identity prism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 466350.0,
      "end_time": 470216.0,
      "text": "which is something like the sonic identity card of a car."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 473560.0,
      "end_time": 477969.0,
      "text": "And as a third step, we enter the world of the sound design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 479460.0,
      "end_time": 481831.0,
      "text": "where the sound genes are composed"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 481855.0,
      "end_time": 484198.0,
      "text": "and a new archetype is conceived."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 485610.0,
      "end_time": 488730.0,
      "text": "Now let me show you another example"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 488970.0,
      "end_time": 492363.0,
      "text": "of how I transform a sound field into a melody."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 493847.0,
      "end_time": 496561.0,
      "text": "Think that I am a violin player on stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 496586.0,
      "end_time": 498332.0,
      "text": "If I would start to play the violin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 498356.0,
      "end_time": 502332.0,
      "text": "I would generate a sound field which would propagate in this hall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 502356.0,
      "end_time": 506940.0,
      "text": "and at some point, the sound field would hit the side walls"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 506119.0,
      "end_time": 509688.0,
      "text": "and would be scattered all over the place."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 509712.0,
      "end_time": 511293.0,
      "text": "And this is how it looked like."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 511317.0,
      "end_time": 517164.0,
      "text": "Some time ago, I captured several ways of sound to hit side walls."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 518321.0,
      "end_time": 522424.0,
      "text": "And last year, I was asked by the Bavarian Radio Symphony Orchestra"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 522448.0,
      "end_time": 526280.0,
      "text": "to compose ringtones that they were going to play."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 526820.0,
      "end_time": 531203.0,
      "text": "So one of them, I had the idea to start from this sound field."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 531728.0,
      "end_time": 533622.0,
      "text": "I took a section,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 533646.0,
      "end_time": 536407.0,
      "text": "I superimposed the section over the distribution"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 536432.0,
      "end_time": 538706.0,
      "text": "of the musicians onstage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 538730.0,
      "end_time": 541560.0,
      "text": "and then I followed the blooming of the sound field"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 541584.0,
      "end_time": 543700.0,
      "text": "by means of three parameters:"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 544146.0,
      "end_time": 545785.0,
      "text": "time, intensity and frequency."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 546996.0,
      "end_time": 551858.0,
      "text": "Then I wrote down all the gradients for each instrument,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 551882.0,
      "end_time": 553473.0,
      "text": "and as you can see, for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 553497.0,
      "end_time": 557959.0,
      "text": "the piece will start with the string section playing very softly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 557983.0,
      "end_time": 563945.0,
      "text": "and then it&#39;s going to have a crescendo as the brasses, the woods will jump in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 563970.0,
      "end_time": 567927.0,
      "text": "and the melody will end with a harp and a piano"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 567951.0,
      "end_time": 570125.0,
      "text": "playing on the highest range."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 574457.0,
      "end_time": 576800.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s listen how it sounded like."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 579495.0,
      "end_time": 586359.0,
      "text": "(Ethereal music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 596240.0,
      "end_time": 597390.0,
      "text": "(Music ends)"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 599895.0,
      "end_time": 603122.0,
      "text": "So this is the sound of my alarm clock, actually, in the morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 603146.0,
      "end_time": 604295.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 605707.0,
      "end_time": 608660.0,
      "text": "And now let&#39;s go back to electric cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 609338.0,
      "end_time": 614781.0,
      "text": "And let&#39;s listen to the first example that I showed you."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 620890.0,
      "end_time": 627890.0,
      "text": "(Hum)"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 628600.0,
      "end_time": 633680.0,
      "text": "And now I would like to show you how a potential sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 633704.0,
      "end_time": 638473.0,
      "text": "based on the sound genetics for electric cars, could sound like."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 639926.0,
      "end_time": 643513.0,
      "text": "(Ethereal music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 643537.0,
      "end_time": 649837.0,
      "text": "(Pitch rises with acceleration)"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 652365.0,
      "end_time": 659135.0,
      "text": "Cars are a metaphor of time, distance and journey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 659159.0,
      "end_time": 662280.0,
      "text": "of setting out and returning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 662304.0,
      "end_time": 665840.0,
      "text": "of anticipation and adventure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 665109.0,
      "end_time": 670244.0,
      "text": "but, at the same time, of intelligence and complexity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 670268.0,
      "end_time": 673234.0,
      "text": "of human intuition and accomplishment."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 673258.0,
      "end_time": 675750.0,
      "text": "And the sound has to glorify all that."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 677690.0,
      "end_time": 681886.0,
      "text": "I see cars both as living creatures"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 681910.0,
      "end_time": 685964.0,
      "text": "and as highly complex performative art installations."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 687984.0,
      "end_time": 691585.0,
      "text": "The sounds that we envision through sound genetics"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 691609.0,
      "end_time": 695287.0,
      "text": "allow us not only to celebrate this complexity"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 696735.0,
      "end_time": 701497.0,
      "text": "but also to make the world a more elegant and safe space."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 702700.0,
      "end_time": 703222.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 703246.0,
      "end_time": 706324.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}